<figureCitation id="6A30C3033D527E06536E89B9C7B75B3E" captionStart="Figures 12–16" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figures 12 - 16. Sphecodes biroi Friese, female, paralectotype 12 head, frontal view 13 vertex, dorso-lateral view 14 mesosoma, dorsal view 15 metasoma, dorsal view 16 labels. Scale bars: 1.0 mm (12, 14, 15), 0.5 mm (13)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.937.51708.figures12-16" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/416776" pageId="0" pageNumber="31">12a</figureCitation>
